additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. This device is battery operated. Use only alkaline non-rechargeable batteries. Ensure battery is inserted correctly, aligning the (+) and (-) terminals as indicated. Do not expose the battery to water, fire or high temperatures. Do not cause a short-circuit. If any leakage from the battery is noted, remove it immediately and remove any leaked material. Remove the battery if the device is not in use for a long period of time. If you will be away from home for more than a week, turn off the device.
